import '../App.css' const Cover = () => { return (

Dear Sir / Ma'am,

    With a strong background as a Full Stack Web Developer, I bring to the table a proven track record of
delivering top-notch projects and a versatile skill set encompassing cutting-edge technologies.
    Throughout my career, I have consistently demonstrated my ability to successfully complete projects
with precision and efficiency. I am committed to delivering high-quality websites within specified
timelines.
   My time at Bloom Tech has equipped me with the skills necessary to excel in dynamic and fast-paced
environments. I recently completed Bloom Tech's Full Stack Software Engineering course, achieving the
remarkable feat of finishing an 18-month program ahead of schedule. This accomplishment not only
showcases my dedication but also underscores my ability to work effectively as a team player.
   I am genuinely excited about the opportunity to leverage my skills and experience to make meaningful
contributions to your team's success. I am confident that my technical proficiency, problem-solving
abilities, and dedication to excellence align perfectly with your company's goals and values.
   I eagerly anticipate the opportunity to discuss how my qualifications align with your organization's
needs in more detail. Thank you for considering my application.

Sincerely,
Michael Marconi

) } export default Cover;
